body:
### Eastern Taco
WHETHER YOUR A FORD F250 3/4 TON ON STOCK RIMS, SKODA ROOMSTER TDI OR WHOLE LOTTA LADA. THERE IS ALWAYS A PILE OF SPECIAL STUFF FOR YOU TO HAUL AWAY.

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

PITCHES, PILES and CLIPPINGS

### EASTERN FILP
Hummus, Onion, Tomatoes, Parsley, Sirene

### WESTERN FOLD
Black Beans, Onion, Tomatoes, Cilantro, Cheddar

### LITTLE BEAN CHEESER
Kids love fart jokes, refried beans and cheddar cheese

### BLACK HOLE
A Journey that Begins Where Everything Ends - Black Bean Chilaquiles, Tortilla Chips, Sirene

### VILLAGE MODERN TORTILLA SOUP
Simplistic and Complexity collide on this Confluence of Regionalism - Life lessons, drunk in love and whatever else we have in the kitchen that day

### JOAQUIN FAN
Seasonal, but kinda more summertime - Sliced Tri-tip & Roasted Jalape√±os

### SMUGGLERS SLAW
Rhodope Inspired Bedrock / Pork Shoulder with Secrets

### BLACK ORPHEUS
Contrast in Skinny Jeans. Chipotle Pressurized Black Beans in Art House Style

### F250 3/4 TON
Tight Wranglers. Refried Pinto Beans in Mustang Style

### GARBANANZA'S IN VITA STYLE
Lemon Pepper Garlic Pressurized Chickpeas

### SNOWBUSH
Parsly, Sirene

### TERRACE TOMATOES WITH KNIFE
End of the Summer Tomatoes, Salt

### SEASONAL RIVERBED
Oven Roasted Vegetables

### STONE RUN
Cubed Oven Crispy Potatoes

### BLUE PEPPERS
Fresh Market Peppers Fillet Stuffed with Blue

### NOMADIC NACHOS
Lost? So are we. These epic late night drunken fried gnocchi nuggets hooked up with sirene on paper bag bed...

### GWAKA RAFT
Still lost, but supper hungry and sober? We know the life raft just for you. Hand chopped guacamole, with all the life preservers. Your choice of corn tortilla or chips.

### REVOLUTION SALAD
Diced Roasted Potatoes, Red Pepper, Green Pepper, Smoked Kashkaval, Parsley

### SHOPSKA IN A MIDWEST STYLE
Iceberg, Black Beans, Diced Roasted Potatoes, White Onion, Red Pepper, Chilled Tomato Pepper Riverbed, Diced Tomatoes, Sirene (pulled pork optional)
